===============================

Core Environment

===============================

NODE_ENV=production

Deployment environment

Options: nodejs | docker | vercel | cloudflare-workers | render

ANIWATCH_API_DEPLOYMENT_ENV=render

===============================

Server Config

===============================

ANIWATCH_API_PORT=4000

Rate limiting (milliseconds)

ANIWATCH_API_WINDOW_MS=1800000
ANIWATCH_API_MAX_REQS=6

===============================

CORS

===============================

Comma-separated domains (no spaces)

Example:

https://your-site.com,https://another-site.com

ANIWATCH_API_CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=*

===============================

Hostname (optional, for rate limiting)

===============================

ANIWATCH_API_HOSTNAME=beat-anime-api-3.onrender.com

===============================

Redis (optional)

===============================

Example:

rediss://default:password@host:6379

ANIWATCH_API_REDIS_CONN_URL=

===============================

CDN Cache Config

===============================

ANIWATCH_API_S_MAXAGE=60
ANIWATCH_API_STALE_WHILE_REVALIDATE=30

===============================

Admin Secret (optional)

===============================

TATAKAI_ADMIN_API_SECRET=DarkPlusX2

===============================

HiAnime Scraper Domain

===============================

aniwatchtv.to is the OLD/DEAD default - MUST set this to hianimez.to

ANIWATCH_DOMAIN=hianime.cv

Optional: AJAX version prefix (default /v2 for hianimez.to, leave blank for 9animetv.to)

ANIWATCH_AJAX_VERSION_PREFIX=/v2
